# MISC::IS_NEXT_WEATHER_TYPE

## Parameters
* **STRING** weather

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Checks if the next weather type (the one we are currently interpolating towards) is the same as the string passed
